---
import PageHead from '@/components/PageHead.astro'
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout class="max-w-3xl">
  <PageHead slot="head" title="Home" />
  <section class="rounded-lg border">
    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6">
      <h3 class="text-3xl leading-none font-medium">al·gno·n</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">/ˈælɡ.nɒn/</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 pt-0">
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-2 text-sm">
        algnon comes from the idea of slow, steady change — the kind that
        reshapes things around you without trying to be noticed. the name sits
        in that space between thinking and feeling, between what you build and
        what slips beyond your plans.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
        it’s a reminder that creating isn’t just making something work. it’s
        paying attention to how each choice quietly shifts the world a little.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
